history.content: You do have reserved seats. Although if you're put on the waitlist that means all the reserved seats are taken by other eecs. If an eecs major drop the class, the reserved seats will open so you might get off the waitlist faster even at #230. Keep in mind that 61B will try its best to expand and accept everybody who wants to take the class.

I'm an EECS major who tried enrolling for CS61B for Fall 2020 during Phase 2 enrollment. I was put on waitlist #239. Does anyone know if EECS majors get preference/reserved seats? I am looking to take this class with the "Remote" or "Internet/Online" option as I'll be taking it from home.
history.subject: Is 61B closed for Fall 2020?
